{"tid":324571,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[職場新手]有無CHING解釋下咩是長短周","createTime":"2017-07-16T13:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T13:55:58.000Z","uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d90b5fd96226ff7affcb28396508f7776bb2538c","tid":324571,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"長週 = 要返星期六, 一星期返5天半, 就是長週了. <br />\n短週 = 原用返星期六, 一星期返5天, 就是短週了. <br />\n通常是一個星期長週, 下一個星期就短週, 如此類推... <br />\n吾會全公司短週的, 通常是一半員工返長週, 一半返短週, 咁公司就吾會無人做野啦. <br />\n有D公司有長短週, 是福利的一種, 用來吸引員工. <br />\n點解吾全部改做返5天?? 因為有D老板想增加福利, 但又吾想星期六無人返工, 因為好多大陸工廠或客人星期六都要返工的.<br />\n睇完都唔明,閱讀理解拎U"},{"pid":"893ac6fe809a8ed3af6b7615d9cce619746eef24","tid":324571,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"開錯台SORRY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001a3aa6ed129881b0aa4a3e2ec3433c38f6c854","tid":324571,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"0757a1e8265e5edda35e9e916d285b8f76aa7cec","tid":324571,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾你老母</blockquote><br />\n好明顯COPY人地-.-...."},{"pid":"06f4512282cc5a74898deb2d5b8e440f58e7f21f","tid":324571,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吾你老母</blockquote><br />\n好明顯COPY人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"29d1fa0d951856cda9a6098a244f5a33d9446eea","tid":324571,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"吾你老母死臭撚"}]}